 preceding earthquakes. II. determination of epicenter and magnitude\n |journal=Tectonophysics\n |volume=110|issue=1|pages=99\u2013125\n |doi=10.1016/0040-1951(84)90060-X\n|bibcode=1984Tectp.110...99V\n }}\n*{{Citation\n |first1= P. |last1= Varotsos\n |year= 2006\n |title= What happened before the last five strong earthquakes in Greece\n |journal= Proc. Jpn. Acad. Ser. B\n |volume= 82 |issue= 2 |pages= 86\u201391\n |doi= 10.2183/pjab.82.86\n |pmid= 25792775\n |bibcode= 2006PJAB...82...86V \n|pmc= 4323052\n }}\n*{{Citation\n |first1= P. |last1= Varotsos\n |first2= K. |last2= Alexopoulos\n |first3= M. |last3= Lazaridou\n |year= 1993\n |title= Latest aspects of earthquake prediction in Greece based on seismic electric signals, II\n |journal= Tectonophysics\n |volume= 224 |issue= 1\n |pages= 1\u201337\n |bibcode = 1993Tectp.224....1V\n |doi = 10.1016/0040-1951(93)90055-O\n|url= http://www.gt-crust.ru/jour/article/view/220\n }}\n*{{Citation\n |first1= P. |last1= Varotsos\n |first2= K. |last2= Alexopoulos\n |first3= K. |last3= Nomicos\n |year= 1981a\n |title= Seismic electric currents\n |journal= Proceedings of the Academy of Athens\n |volume= 56 |pages= 277\u2013286\n}}\n*{{Citation\n |first1= P. |last1= Varotsos\n |first2= K. |last2= Alexopoulos\n |first3= K. |last3= Nomicos\n |year= 1981b\n |title= Seven-hour precursors to earthquakes determined from telluric currents \n |journal= Praktika of the Academy of Athens |volume= 56 |pages= 417\u2013433\n}}\n*{{Citation\n |first1= P. |last1= Varotsos\n |first2= K. |last2= Alexopoulos\n |first3= K. |last3= Nomicos\n |year= 1982\n |title= Electrotelluric precursors to earthquakes\n |journal= Proceedings of the Academy of Athens\n |volume= 57 |pages= 341\u2013363\n}}\n*{{Citation\n |first1= P. |last1= Varotsos\n |first2= K. |last2= Alexopoulos\n |first3= K. |last3= Nomicos\n |first4= M. |last4= Lazaridou\n |year= 1986\n |title= Earthquake prediction and electric signals\n |journal= Nature \n |volume= 322 |issue= 6075 |page= 120 